A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180609%2Fbkntw-20180609000032479-0609_04011_001.html&d=0R7mf%2BBld8gkaJqELX1Qy4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=169128b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20180609/bkntw-20180609000032479-0609_04011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nudn聯合新聞網：母放任女兒全裸公園玩耍 挨批「家長有病嗎？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7320/3186461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7320%2F3186461&d=0R7mf%2BBld8gkaJqELX1Qy4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6177fc5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7320/3186461</a><br />\n<br />\nTVBS：任人看？放「全裸女兒」公園玩　路人批：家長有病<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/life/934226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Flife%2F934226&d=0R7mf%2BBld8gkaJqELX1Qy4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ca6e1d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/life/934226</a><br />\n<br />\nETT：女兒脫光爬樹露屁屁！媽淡定坐公園聊天　家長路過看傻眼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180608/1186346.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180608%2F1186346.htm&d=0R7mf%2BBld8gkaJqELX1Qy4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=d80ae667\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180608/1186346.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4b3294713c945b67edf8ddd68e26f4d641b4ba58","tid":695391,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"840763daf09bda95d5b241157625881b8c49be34","tid":695391,"uid":64701,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"藝術家Sally Mann有輯相都係影低子女冇著衫嘅狀態<br />\n有人批評係兒童色情<br />\nSally Mann反駁，兒童嘅身體本應唔會聯想到色情方面，裸體係自然嘅狀態，子女可以喺大自然上自由活動，古時候嘅人一樣會咁做，會聯想到色情方面根本係讀者同批評者自身問題。作為父母，面對子女裸體係好自然嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n先唔講個老母有冇錯，呢一刻網上嘅道德審判的確可以傷害嗰位小妹妹。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"父母面對自己子女裸體係好正常，<br />\n但公園入面嘅其他人呢？<br />\n<br />\n引起社會嘩然，就代表社會有色情目光去看待個女仔裸體爬樹/影小朋友裸照？<br />\n<br />\n豬心記者都提出過，就係有啲父母好鐘意用記錄小朋友成長每一刻為由，將小朋友咩樣都擺哂上網，包括裸體。<br />\n<br />\n但有無諗過小朋友係點諗，佢地鐘唔鐘意父母咩都擺上網度share？點解小朋友就唔可以有自己嘅私隱？<br />\n<br />\n講返今次呢件事，當下小朋友覺得件衫濕咗水好唔舒服想除，係咪畀佢除就一定好？個媽媽係點樣肯定佢當下畀小朋友自主，由佢除衫，就係令佢解放自由？個媽媽覺得人著唔著衫，係身體自主，自由選擇咁簡單？"},{"pid":"5072051472b85acb0cc29bc872de1b0545ff0ecd","tid":695391,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"在場影相嘅人係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細路都好影"},{"pid":"2ac0ec2969839ae4cafb44281c103ea669857abe","tid":695391,"uid":7550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8180360c5c75762f6efccbaf10659739d33c5140","tid":695391,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43527d8c9929ece73d82382e4334cd66ad089ac9","tid":695391,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"我好好奇，到底支持身體自主嘅人係點樣看待道德呢樣野？係咪覺得呢啲野都係父權？係咪所有野只要係自主就無問題？<br />\n<br />\n有時當見到有人講強姦案，就話受害人自己夜返、著得小布，會引起兇徒本能，而衝動犯案，我都會覺得好嬲。覺得佢地係用本能去合理化兇徒嘅暴行，而正常人就要因為呢啲兇徒而限制自由。<br />\n<br />\n但另一方面，有啲人只要係身體自主同充權，就做咩都無問題，包括做性工作者同慶祝墮胎。<br />\n<br />\n咁極端真係睇到人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfa870d0db3c068b7b9ec14274e752c798997b0","tid":695391,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5072051472b85acb0cc29bc872de1b0545ff0ecd","tid":695391,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"在場影相嘅人係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細路都好影"},"